{"tid":1051382,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"歐央行向銀行再放水　押後加息","createTime":"2019-03-07T14:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T14:43:00.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"caf19466457745bb6293ae0a885e4888bb6d41bf","tid":1051382,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190307/photo/bkn-20190307204548690-0307_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190307215543\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190307204548690-0307_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190307215543&h=70737de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年底才結束量化寬鬆(QE)措施的歐洲央行周四(7日)議息後宣布，再向歐元區銀行業「放水」，由9月起提供新一筆低息貸款─定向長期再融資操作(TLTRO)。該行並改變利率前瞻指引，承諾維持低息的日期，由今年夏天押後至今年底。<br />\n<br />\n此外，歐央行一如預期宣布維持基準利率於零水平，邊際貸款利率及存款利率亦分別不變於0.25厘及負0.4厘。<br />\n<br />\n歐央行行長德拉吉稍後將召開記者會，為今次議息決定解畫，並發表最新經濟及通脹預測。"},{"pid":"fb3d71d248ac01729d041d16af0d9d0add528433","tid":1051382,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"樓價又升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3732af06a18ce50207e886b4722c674d2dc7b83f","tid":1051382,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"QE永無止竟"},{"pid":"017b22cfc6843658581e972f440f8bfb4ee053c8","tid":1051382,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"印鈔機is coming"}]}